{"tid":2153975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為建島國數據中心 任北京竊密不設防","createTime":"2020-08-13T01:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T01:04:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f201f1911fdffaa695ef396b69dcc5ecf61dd324","tid":2153975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200813/DK6A52OC47RBS2WZ4JLOGSWBBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200813%2FDK6A52OC47RBS2WZ4JLOGSWBBA%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=9f3c8a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200813%2FDK6A52OC47RBS2WZ4JLOGSWBBA%2F&h=13eab9af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200813/DK6A52OC47RBS2WZ4JLOGSWBBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華為建島國數據中心 任北京竊密不設防<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備製造商華為多年被指涉嫌洩漏客戶機密及進行間諜活動，現在終出現第一份有力證據。澳洲發表網絡安全報告指，華為負責建造巴布亞新畿內亞（Papua New Guinea）的國家數據中心，被揭使用脆弱的加密軟件和過期的防火牆，給予北京遠端存取，如入無人之境。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：印度搜洗黑錢中資機構 拘一華人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J9lH_Qf4mHzWFHRg2ovrY0bfCHM=/640x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZXNFYZRMLPEC74DF42GOPNKODE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ9lH_Qf4mHzWFHRg2ovrY0bfCHM%3D%2F640x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZXNFYZRMLPEC74DF42GOPNKODE.jpg&h=6da55fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為面對美國制裁，前景堪虞。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防火牆4年前已過期<br />\n<br />\n該份報告長達65頁，指巴布亞新畿內亞的莫爾茲比港國家數據中心（The Port Moresby data centre）是由北京提供資金、華為。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華為手機業務亦面臨大挑戰，日前華為高層承認受制於美國制裁，台積電已。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲《金融評論》/中央社"}]}